Both \eqn{\Pr(\mathrm{Go})} and \eqn{\Pr(\mathrm{NoGo})} are
monotone non-increasing functions of \eqn{\gamma}.  The optimal
\eqn{\gamma_{\mathrm{go}}} is the \emph{smallest} grid value
crossing below \code{target_go}.  The optimal
